# ğŸ‘¥ Advanced User Management System

A complete, production-ready web application built with Flask and SQLite for managing users with authentication, search, filtering, and pagination.

## âœ¨ Features

### Core Features
- âœ… **User Authentication** - Secure admin login system with session management
- âœ… **CRUD Operations** - Create, Read, Update, Delete users
- âœ… **User Dashboard** - Overview with statistics (total, active, inactive users)
- âœ… **Search & Filtering** - Search by name/email, filter by status
- âœ… **Sorting** - Sort users by ID, name, email, or date added
- âœ… **Pagination** - Handle large datasets with page navigation
- âœ… **Input Validation** - Email format, phone number, and data validation
- âœ… **User Status** - Mark users as active/inactive
- âœ… **Responsive Design** - Beautiful modern UI that works on all devices

### User Fields
- Name (required)
- Email (unique, required)
- Phone (optional)
- Address (optional)
- Status (active/inactive)
- Created Date
- Updated Date

