## ğŸ“± Responsive Design

The application is fully responsive and works on:
- Desktop computers (1024px and above)
- Tablets (768px to 1024px)
- Mobile phones (below 768px)

## ğŸš€ Advanced Features

### Pagination
- 10 users per page (configurable)
- Navigation buttons to move between pages
- Maintains search and filter state across pages

### Search Functionality
- Real-time search by name or email
- Case-insensitive matching
- Works with pagination and filters

### Status Management
- Toggle between active and inactive
- Filter users by status
- Visual status badges

### Sorting Options
- Sort by ID (latest first)
- Sort by Name (A-Z)
- Sort by Email
- Sort by Created Date

## ğŸ”§ Customization

### Change Admin Password
Edit `app.py` and modify:
```python
conn.execute("INSERT OR IGNORE INTO admins (username, password) VALUES (?, ?)", 
             ('admin', 'your_new_password'))
```

### Modify Items Per Page
Edit `app.py` and change:
```python
ITEMS_PER_PAGE = 10  # Change to desired number
```

### Change Application Port
Edit the last line in `app.py`:
```python
app.run(debug=True, port=5001)  # Change port number
```

## ğŸ§ª Testing the Application

### Test Data Entry
